## DevSecOps Checklist

- [ ] Container image scanned for HIGH and CRITICAL findings before ECR push
- [ ] Approved image pushed to ECR and deployed to ECS only after the scan passes
- [ ] Secrets stored in AWS Secrets Manager or Parameter Store
- [ ] WAF enabled for public traffic
- [ ] IAM reviewed for least privilege
- [ ] Runtime tags include owner, account, region, and customer
- [ ] CloudWatch logs and metrics enabled
- [ ] Dashboards and alerts available to support teams
- [ ] Runbooks prepared for deployment, rollback, and incident handling

